    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "Thursday evening, October I, the\nYoung Women's Christian association\nwill hold a public reception at their\nnew home in the Symons block. The\nassociation has now a membership of\n176, and in having the reception Mrs\nc. c. Potter, the secretary. hopes on\nthat evening to start a campaign\nwith a view to charging the scope\nof the work and increasing the active\nmembership."
    }
  ]
